*<div id="function.imagecolorclosestalpha" class="refentry">  <div class="refnamediv">   <h1 class="refname">imagecolorclosestalpha</h1>   <p class="verinfo">(PHP 4 &gt;= 4.0.6, PHP 5, PHP 7)</p><p class="refpurpose"><span class="refname">imagecolorclosestalpha</span> &mdash; <span class="dc-title">取得与指定的颜色加透明度最接近的颜色</span></p>   </div>  <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 description" id="refsect1-function.imagecolorclosestalpha-description">   <h3 class="title">说明</h3>  <div class="methodsynopsis dc-description" style="border:1px gray;padding-left:5px;background:#232525">    <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766">int</span> <span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832"><strong>imagecolorclosestalpha</strong></span>     ( <span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766">resource</span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">$image</span></span>    , <span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766">int</span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">$red</span></span>    , <span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766">int</span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">$green</span></span>    , <span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766">int</span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">$blue</span></span>    , <span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766">int</span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">$alpha</span></span>    )</div>    <p class="para rdfs-comment">    返回图像调色板中与指定的 <acronym title="Red-Green-Blue">RGB</acronym> 值以及    <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">alpha</span> 深度最“接近”的颜色。   </p>  </div>   <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 parameters" id="refsect1-function.imagecolorclosestalpha-parameters">   <h3 class="title">参数</h3>   <span>    <dl>      <dt> <span class