/**
*<div id="function.imagelayereffect" class="refentry">  <div class="refnamediv">   <h1 class="refname">imagelayereffect</h1>   <p class="verinfo">(PHP 4 &gt;= 4.3.0, PHP 5, PHP 7)</p><p class="refpurpose"><span class="refname">imagelayereffect</span> &mdash; <span class="dc-title">设定 alpha 混色标志以使用绑定的 libgd 分层效果   </span></p>   </div>  <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 description" id="refsect1-function.imagelayereffect-description">   <h3 class="title">说明</h3>     <div class="methodsynopsis dc-description" style="border:1px gray;padding-left:5px;background:#232525">    <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766">bool</span> <span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832"><strong>imagelayereffect</strong></span>     ( <span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766">resource</span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">$image</span></span>    , <span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766">int</span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">$effect</span></span>    )</div>    <p class="para rdfs-comment">    设定 alpha 混色标志以使用绑定的 libgd 分层效果。   </p>  </div>   <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 parameters" id="refsect1-function.imagelayereffect-parameters">   <h3 class="title">参数</h3>   <span>    <dl>      <dt> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">image</span></dt>  <dd> <p class="para">由图象创建函数(例如<span class="function">{@link imagecreatetruecolor()}</span>)返回的图象资源。</p></dd>            <dt> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">effect</span></dt>       <dd>        <p class="para">        One of the following constants:        <dl>                    <dt> <strong><span>IMG_EFFECT_REPLACE</span></strong></dt>           <dd>            <span class="simpara">            Use pixel replacement (equivalent of passing <strong><span>TRUE</span></strong> to            <span